yet have a planned date for a JBuilder 2005 plugin.  More information on the 
status of the JBuilder support is available at:

I will keep this report open in order to notify you of updates to the status 
of the JBuilder support.
*** Bug 77313 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***

Improving JBuilder support is not planned in the near future, in particular
since we can expect more interoperability with JBuilder as they move features
onto Eclipse.
